HEADWORD: Gillhouse
<hw>Gill"house`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A shop where gill is
sold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thee shall each alehouse, thee each <qex>gillhouse</qex>
mourn.</q> <rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gillian</ent>⟦br⟧
